      "line": 39,
      "message": "That was intentional - I wanted to base our released SDNC docker on the released version of CCSDK to make sure we don't run into issues later if the staging versions are purged.  The problem was that I'd inadvertently omitted the alpine-j17 docker image from the list I'd released, which caused our build to fail. I fixed that and released that image, which now fixed this build.",
